="round" width="24" height="24" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke="currentColor" role="img" stroke-width="2" class="svgicon icon_play" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polygon points="10 8 16 12 10 16 10 8"></polygon></svg> Run tool</button></div></div></div><div class="columns"><div class="left_col column"><div class="formatted_description user_formatted"><h2>About this Project</h2><p>This is the prototype map generator built with the Pokemon style Monster Catching Framework I am developing. I will be adding to it over the coming months. I have no timeline on when this will be finished, but I intend to make a kind of roguelike with it where you can generate a unique region and play though gyms + elite four.</p>
<h2>Future Plans</h2>
<p>My priority as a developer right now is to finish the RPG framework I am using to build this map generator. Right now the framework is very rough and the battle system is unfinished. Once I have finished creating a small playable (and hopefully fun) game with this framework I will focus on this project more and turn this idea into a commercial game.</p>
